## Model Installation Guide

Go to your ComfyUI installation directory and install these models in the correct subfolders as indicated below:

### **Diffusion Model**
- [DreamShaper_8_pruned.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Lykon/DreamShaper/resolve/main/DreamShaper_8_pruned.safetensors)

### **AnimateDiff Models**

### **LoRA**
- [AnimateLCM_sd15_t2v_lora.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/wangfuyun/AnimateLCM/resolve/main/AnimateLCM_sd15_t2v_lora.safetensors)

### **Upscale Model**
- [2x-sudo-UltraCompact.pth](https://openmodeldb.info/models/2x-sudo-UltraCompact)

### **ControlNet**
- [control_v1p_sd15_qrcode_monster_v2.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/monster-labs/control_v1p_sd15_qrcode_monster/resolve/main/v2/control_v1p_sd15_qrcode_monster_v2.safetensors)
- [v3_sd15_sparsectrl_rgb.ckpt](https://huggingface.co/guoyww/animatediff/resolve/main/v3_sd15_sparsectrl_rgb.ckpt)

### **VAE**
- [vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/stabilityai/sd-vae-ft-mse-original/resolve/main/vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned.safetensors)

### **Motion Adapters**
- [v3_sd15_adapter.ckpt](https://huggingface.co/guoyww/animatediff/resolve/main/v3_sd15_adapter.ckpt)


### **IP-Adapter**
- [ip-adapter-plus_sd15.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/h94/IP-Adapter/resolve/main/models/ip-adapter-plus_sd15.safetensors)

### **CLIP Vision Model**
- [CLIP-ViT-H-14-laion2B-s32B-b79K.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/laion/CLIP-ViT-H-14-laion2B-s32B-b79K/resolve/main/model.safetensors) (rename it from model.safetensors to CLIP-ViT-H-14-laion2B-s32B-b79K.safetensors)
